text.section:
A board member shall be automatically removed from the board and a vacancy shall occur when:
An auctioneer member of the board ceases to be a licensed auctioneer;
A nonlicensed member of the board acquires a license regulated by the board;
A board member enters a plea of guilty, an Alford plea, a plea of no contest to, or has been convicted of, any felony, and the time for appeal has passed or the judgment of conviction has been finally affirmed on appeal; or
A board member ceases to be a resident of the Commonwealth of Kentucky.
